be.kuleuven.cs.som.taglet
Class NoteTaglet

java.lang.Object
  be.kuleuven.cs.som.taglet.OOPTaglet
      be.kuleuven.cs.som.taglet.NoteTaglet
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.sun.tools.doclets.Taglet
public class NoteTaglet
extends OOPTaglet

The NoteTaglet is an OOPTaglet, used for notes, which can be used anywhere. It is used with the keyword "note" and the header for the subsection will be "Note:". Even notes can have a formal part.

NoteTaglet should be used on tags that are formatted as follows:

@note     informal note
          | formal part line 1
          | formal part line 2
          ...
The formal part can be left out. The output will be of the form:

Note:
informal note
formally: formal part line 1
formal part line 2

Author:
Koen Vanderkimpen
